    - to-json — codemap-native JSON dump
    - to-graphml — XML for yEd / Cytoscape / NetworkX
    - to-gexf — Gephi format with per-EntityKind viz colors

  Output formats let users round-trip codemap's heterogeneous graph
  into dedicated viz tools when dot/mermaid aren't enough (force-
  directed layouts, interactive filtering, time-series).

